A tale of triumphs and sorrows, the Sixth War of the Dwarves and Orcs ended with the battle of Azanulbizar. There, at long last, Azog revealed himself before the east-gate of Moria. After much blood was shed, Azog was slain by D치in II, now dubbed 'Ironfoot', and the war was ended.
